- to compile the ccm26ToFoam utility under the ESI version (tested at v1912)
  - source the openfoam env.
  - export the following variable:
        export LIBCCMIO_LIB_DIR=/$(pwd)/libccmio-2.6.1/lib
  - compile (wclean;  wmake)
  - copy the binary files from libccmio-2.6.1/lib to your FOAM_USER_LIBBIN 
